  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "There are a number of changes needed to support multiple backends in Rook. Currently with only Ceph, some ceph-specified naming and design have seeped in. We need a design doc that lays out the basic approach that will be used in Rook.\r\n- CRDs should be factored\r\n- Source tree layout should have backend-specific folders\r\n\r\n#1358 started the refactoring effort. Related efforts are happening in #1346.",
